y-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.316455696202528%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRkIAAABXRUJQVlA4IDYAAABQAwCdASoUAAUAPtFYpkwoJSOiMAgBABoJZwAAW+s26GbaAAD+8BuuQWmFheXEVU8qInPCAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, loading, overlay\"\n        title=\"React, loading, overlay\"\n        src=\"/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/8aab1/loading-overlay.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/81b7c/loading-overlay.webp 158w,\n/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/6ea66/loading-overlay.webp 315w,\n/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/8aab1/loading-overlay.webp 630w,\n/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/a70f5/loading-overlay.webp 945w,\n/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/4ef06/loading-overlay.webp 1260w,\n/static/21e92dda5a2865f17477c8811690ac6d/1bc7b/loading-overlay.webp 1364w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best 👍</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to make mui table with loading overlay in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"March 07, 2024","description":"Example of make mui table with loading overlay in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to align left pagination of mui table in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-03-08-how-to-align-left-pagination-of-mui-table-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to align center pagination of mui table in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-03-07-how-to-align-center-pagination-of-mui-table-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-03-07-how-to-make-mui-table-with-loading-overlay-in-react-